 eines Institutionengefüges dafür geben, daß heute rund ein Drittel aller Staaten bikamerale Parlamente haben.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 4aInternationaler Vergleich. 4aZweite Kammer. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / General.2bisacsh1 aBerndt, Uwe, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBraune, Florian, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCordes, Sandra, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDegener, Ursula, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEith, Ulrich, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFallend, Franz, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFroehling, Catherine Isabel, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGebauer, Bernt, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHaas, Christoph M., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHaas, Christoph M., eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aKaiser, André, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMaubach, Franko, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNolting, Armin K., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRiescher, Gisela, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRiescher, Gisela, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aRosenzweig, Beate, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRuß, Sabine, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRuß, Sabine, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aSeisselberg, Jörg, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relat